Geralt of Rivia is a character from the Witcher series and was added to Super Smash Bros. Ultimate in 2019 as a playable DLC character. Geralt is a versatile fighter who uses his sword and magical abilities to take down his opponents. He is also able to use his signs, which are a form of magic, to stun his enemies and create openings for his attacks. Geralt's inclusion in Super Smash Bros. Ultimate was a surprise to many fans, but his popularity among gamers and his unique playstyle make him a welcome addition to the game.